Updates

GetLNMP 1.0

Only download files from its corresponding website by default
Only support Redhat/Rocky/AlmaLinux/Oracle Linux and Debian/ubuntu
Added Php 8.4 and 8.5
Added MariaDB 11.4 and 11.8
Optimized installation of Nginx, Acme.sh, redis, memcached
Removed support for PHP 5.6-7.2
Removed support for Apache 2.2
Removed support for Centos
Removed support for MariaDB 5.5
Removed support for Mysql 5.7
Many other optimizations...